reviewText: My 2 year old is a little young for it. I think she will enjoy it more by age 4 or 5. However, I enjoyed it.
My 3 yr old grandson wants to watch it over and over
The DVD inside the Homecoming Kids Camp Out box was Homecoming Kids Singalong. So, the product I received was not the product I thought I was buying.
Very good storyline. My 5 year old g'daughter enjoys it very much. Watches it at least once a day when visiting g'parents. If the timing is right will watch it more than once.
thanks needed the song list which it had and they loved it they have had this vcr since it come out but the song list got destroyed after so many years but this helped
This is my personal favorite Homecoming kids video! When George finds out that folks need ketchup on a camping trip...oh my goodness his look is priceless!

All of the Gaither products are top-notch.  The Homecoming Kids videos are extrodinarily educational.  Some of the children shown are actually the children of the Homecoming Friends (Parents/artists).  Never a worry with the Gaither products.
My young son just loves this video. We have watched it a lot since it came. We will definitely be looking at more Gaither videos for kids. Thanks for getting it to us in a timely manner.
